{"tid":205460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(無恥毒果）22歲阿康月入三萬 載女士會有雪條食?","createTime":"2017-04-17T19:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T05:54:42.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09c2646de0efefabd5d11b9101d66e72bfc21f1f","tid":205460,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T19:56:05.000Z","msg":"【Van佬日與夜】22歲阿康月入三萬 載女士會有雪條食?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n運輸行業競爭激烈，app抽佣制度為人詬病，廣大「尊貴」客人亦要求多多。 <br />\n<br />\n但90後貨Van司機阿康入行短短兩年已月入三萬，無拘束的工作環境更令阿康有一套特別的「待客」秘技及睇法，因此鬧出不少笑話。  <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170416/2_499926_0/-Van%E4%BD%AC%E6%97%A5%E8%88%87%E5%A4%9C-22%E6%AD%B2%E9%98%BF%E5%BA%B7%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%89%E8%90%AC-%E8%BC%89%E5%A5%B3%E5%A3%AB%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%89%E9%9B%AA%E6%A2%9D%E9%A3%9F-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170416%2F2_499926_0%2F-Van%25E4%25BD%25AC%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25A4%259C-22%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%2598%25BF%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2585%25A5%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%2590%25AC-%25E8%25BC%2589%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%259B%25AA%25E6%25A2%259D%25E9%25A3%259F-&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=453ad613\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170416%2F2_499926_0%2F-Van%25E4%25BD%25AC%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25A4%259C-22%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%2598%25BF%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2585%25A5%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%2590%25AC-%25E8%25BC%2589%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%259B%25AA%25E6%25A2%259D%25E9%25A3%259F-&h=883767b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170416/2_499926_0/-Van%E4%BD%AC%E6%97%A5%E8%88%87%E5%A4%9C-22%E6%AD%B2%E9%98%BF%E5%BA%B7%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%89%E8%90%AC-%E8%BC%89%E5%A5%B3%E5%A3%AB%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%89%E9%9B%AA%E6%A2%9D%E9%A3%9F-</a><br />\n下面先係重點：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n註：阿康都係C4V司機，就住壹傳媒嘅訪問，佢今晚出咗呢個聲明回應，我一字不漏噉出，多謝各位留意。<br />\n<br />\n致各位客貨車同業:<br />\n<br />\n近日，本人接受蘋果日報記者專訪，但其後該報於網上公布之片段與當日訪問內容有所差異。<br />\n<br />\n整個訪問歷時約一小時，當中談及行業辛酸及不公平對待之事。遺憾的是，蘋果日報將大部份內容及重點刪去。 <br />\n<br />\n有關收入部份，其實本人於訪問過程中已說明只是營業額並未扣除成本，而本人亦重點提及行業有季節性、農曆新年及長假期後經營困難等問題，可惜於公佈的片段亦遭删去。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報只公佈部份專訪片段，行為涉嫌斷章取義，令本人飽受同業奚落。<br />\n<br />\n然而，經一事長一智，本人得到今次教訓，以後均不會接受「壹傳媒」集團的訪問。<br />\n<br />\n如是次事件令各位同業不安，本人謹此道歉，並感謝各位對今次事件之關注。<br />\n<br />\n而本人不欲再節外生枝，故此不會以任何行動反擊，謝謝。"},{"pid":"9059d9c8067cfa4bd365dbbdbfc2e41fc6bef1e8","tid":205460,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T19:57:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/conradwu/posts/10155303449740774\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fconradwu%2Fposts%2F10155303449740774&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=630812d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/conradwu/posts/10155303449740774</a>"},{"pid":"4f6849d457f3a08c2cc527897c9539179c448627","tid":205460,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T22:10:10.000Z","msg":"唔搵傻仔催谷唔會引到人入局幫手做奴隸呢"},{"pid":"e9e0d150debd471833d471ffcc95d12bd12fd558","tid":205460,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T00:31:37.000Z","msg":"毒果一直都係咁架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca442c0fc4af3ba36148db23ba74868404813fa","tid":205460,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T00:39:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5a59903a5690f582ed2ef9f0bca6b046db4a526","tid":205460,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T01:48:54.000Z","msg":"臨尾個句真係輸撚曬<br />\n<br />\n就算唔打算追究都要加返句「保留追究權利」或「會咨詢法律意見後再作決定」<br />\n<br />\n呢個時勢要識得保護自己權益"},{"pid":"13310dead8f45899d04714d90c846c0b4056a0ce","tid":205460,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T01:57:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>毒果一直都係咁架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n條友係咪坐左廿年<br />\n<br />\n居然唔知毒果作風</blockquote><br />\n經一事蔡一智啦<br />\n<br />\n大把人睇報紙都係直接落肚<br />\n唔會諗下有無多左少左"},{"pid":"7c554b42e75111feb8911bdf3167213432c46a68","tid":205460,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T02:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509475c7ec19fd7d54846ae2df1f62a8ea617888","tid":205460,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9510c001c23519aaa07e456b072698e0bb9c84","tid":205460,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbb02c60cec65eab9672465d786c70e8f6f6ce3","tid":205460,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:43:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc3c034016a0b0336d8b2da46d0db5f676a1a13c","tid":205460,"uid":62070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:54:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}